			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Honestly 3 things we could get to improve us:  
<br />
 
<br />
1.  Scale our pet hps to benefit from the +hps on our gear.  This would be great IMO, but if it's too much to ask for, at least greatly increase pet hps.
<br />

<br />
2.  new pet weapons: snare slow and agro.  A random proc is not overpowering. 
<br />

<br />
3.  command /pet no attack:  it is activated and while pet is in no attack mode, he will only cast spells and taunt his targets. 
<br />

<br />
And much more that other mages have suggested. 
<br />

<br />
As far as dps, I still think we're fine for the most part, if we can get some utility added.  DPS really isn't a big thing anymore and mages can reach high dps totals if they work.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
